Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.35,0:02:57.68,OP-CH1,,0,0,0,,With the blood and emotions that lived in this heart
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.68,0:03:00.44,OP-CH1,,0,0,0,,我不會放棄掙扎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.06,OP-CH1,,0,0,0,,銀色之風
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.81,OP-CH1,,0,0,0,,將此身燃盡
